  "body": "### What's your issue about?\r\nIstanbul is changing the gas costs for balance queries via [EIP-1884](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1884). Since it's significantly easier to query the local balance of the contract, and since that is a pretty wildly used feature that people use, that EIP also _reduces_ the costs for self balance checks via a new opcode.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\nAn optimization should take place that replaces any self balance queries with the `SELFBALANCE` opcode. Either that, or querying it via `self.balance` should directly call this opcode.\r\n\r\nNote: might be best to add this feature via #1230 ruleset switch so that it only uses this optimization under Istanbul rules",
